headline: Welltower Announces Date of Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings Release, Conference Call and Webcast
summary: Welltower® Inc. (NYSE: WELL) today announced it will release fourth quarter 2024 financial results after the close of trading on the New York Stock Exchange on Tuesday, February 11, 2025. The Company will host a conference call and webcast on Wednesday, February 12, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss these results. The Company's earnings release will be available in the Investors section of the Company's website.
